[thinking] I'm pondering whether the static variable `Platform.osType` can be inlined in the `isMac` method. It seems like it might not be a compile-time constant, especially since it’s defined in a static block. I’m also thinking if I need a separate `MacWindowUtils` class, which could be necessary to interface with Mac-specific classes from `com.apple`. I should look into how to set the window's alpha for Mac systems.
[thinking] 
